HOW TO INSTALL
===============

A) Declaration of this plugin in fusiondirectory.conf

<menu>
<section>
  ....
      <plugin acl="board" class="board" />
    </section>
  </menu>

<boardtabs>
    <tab class="board" name="Overview"/>
    <tab class="boardUserAccounts" name="Users"/>
    <tab class="boardSystems" name="Systems"/>
    <tab class="boardUserNetwork" name="Network"/>
</boardtabs>

B) Additional parameter in fusiondirectory.conf

This plugin need 2 additional parameter in fusiondirectory.conf (Location section)

* board_next_expired_account
It is the number of days to analyze the next expired account ( 15 by default)
board_next_expired_account="15"

* board_next_computer_ids_rule
It is the formated rule in order to suggest next unused PC ids
The first parameter is the number of digit
The next parameters is the several prefix of pc Ids
by default it is "4;PC"
it will generate those pc ids : PC01, PC02, PC03
the plugin don't show the already used pc Ids
board_next_computer_ids_rule="7;LYP0;LYP1;LYP2;LYP3;DLNX"
As option you could specify the first ids to use.
ex : 7;LYP0;LYP1=345
will give you
LYP0000;LYP0001;LYP0002...
LYP1345;LYP1346;LYP1347...


